  "detailed_description": "Psychological thriller, where she holds power over you. A lot of victims died here. She made them her slaves to become stronger and more bloodthirsty. Can you resist it in the struggle for survival?<br />\r\nEseapner is an survival-horror game made on blender engine.<br />\r\nWe tried to transform classic horror gameplay into first-person game with highly detailed interiors, textures and lighting.<br />\r\nThis game is result of many years of developing.<br />\r\nIf you like surreal, depressive and dark games, then you'll love Eseapner.",
  "about_the_game": "Psychological thriller, where she holds power over you. A lot of victims died here. She made them her slaves to become stronger and more bloodthirsty. Can you resist it in the struggle for survival?<br />\r\nEseapner is an survival-horror game made on blender engine.<br />\r\nWe tried to transform classic horror gameplay into first-person game with highly detailed interiors, textures and lighting.<br />\r\nThis game is result of many years of developing.<br />\r\nIf you like surreal, depressive and dark games, then you'll love Eseapner.",
